    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in style with this fantastic find! This vehicle is in truly good condition, having been well-maintained and cared for throughout its life. It drives smoothly and looks great, showing only the minor, expected signs of careful use. It's a reliable, high-quality choice for anyone looking for a dependable and attractive ride!",
