      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been treated with lots of love? This beauty is in great shape and ready for its next adventure! It\u2019s been my trusty companion, runs smoothly, and looks fantastic on the road. Perfect for anyone wanting a dependable car without the 'new car' price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re gonna love it!",
      "price": 33500.0,
