    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 987.1 Cayman S is powered by the 3.4L M97.21 flat-six, featuring an optimized VarioCam Plus system for a broad torque curve. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides precise gate engagement, paired with a chassis that benefits from a recent suspension refresh, including new control arm bushings and an alignment to factory spec. Preventative maintenance is current, with a documented high-flow water pump replacement and a recent bore-scoring scope showing clean cylinder walls. Equipped with PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management) and a factory-optional limited-slip differential, the mechanical grip and turn-in response are exceptional. While showing minor cosmetic patina, the powertrain and drivetrain remain in peak operating condition, offering a visceral 7,200 RPM redline experience.",
