    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2016 Porsche Cayman is a stunning example of precision engineering, finished in a timeless Agate Grey Metallic. The exterior retains a brilliant luster, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the front fascia\u2014honest evidence of spirited weekend drives. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and free of odors; the black leather seats are firm and supportive, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s entry bolster. Every button, switch, and dial functions exactly as intended, including the premium Bose sound system and dual-zone climate control. Mechanically, this vehicle has been maintained with an open checkbook, featuring a complete service log from authorized centers. The 2.7L flat-six engine sounds superb, and the PDK transmission shifts with crisp, lightning-fast accuracy. It sits on a set of near-new Michelin Pilot Sport tires and recently underwent a full brake service. This is a reliable, turn-key sports car ready for its next enthusiast owner.",
